nodes.text: The Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi and Senator Dewell Bronk had to change transports on a planet with green colored skies while trying to flee Coruscant following the end of the Clone Wars. Bronk encountered a pair of clone troopers who tried to arrest him on his way to his transport at Pad 560, but Kenobi saved him, allowing him to successfully leave the world.

The planet first appeared in "Incognito," a short story by author John Jackson Miller and illustrated by Chris Scalf, which was published in Star Wars Insider 143 in 2013. The story served as a tie-in to Jackson's novel Kenobi, which was released later that year.
